px; display: inline !important;\">Our Store</a><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"font-size: 14px; display: inline !important;\">About Us</a></a></div><div class=\"navbar-collapse collapse\"><ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/43560/4pc_gold_kit_hopon1.jpg?expires=1752613199&amp;signature=6d31688db17cceacda9fb13121f9fcd66299b0385269da2e51994dbdd09c8345\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table><tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPLETE 4PC KIT - Includes 10\" and 12\" gold pans, a 5\" snuffer bottle, and an 11\" non-metallic scoop - everything you need to start prospecting.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DUAL RIFFLE GOLD PANS -&nbsp; Designed with both deep and fine riffles to effectively capture gold flakes and nuggets during wet or dry panning.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HIGH-SUCTION SNIFTER BOTTLE -&nbsp; Features a secure seal and precision tube for maximum suction power when collecting fine gold from your pan.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE, NON-METALLIC SCOOP - Made from tough nylon plastic with a rubberized grip and high-visibility orange handle; safe to use with metal detectors.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PORTABLE AND FIELD READY - Built-in hanging holes on pans and scoop make it easy to attach to your gear for easy transport on the trail or at the river.</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ASR Outdoor 4pc Gold Panning Kit Gold Pans Snifter Bottle Trowel Prospecting Set</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">24.99</span></h2>\n                <p data-start=\"219\" data-end=\"512\">Get ready to strike gold with this all-in-one 4-piece gold panning kit - perfect for beginners and seasoned prospectors alike! This lightweight, portable set includes two gold pans, a snuffer bottle, and a durable scoop, making it ideal for fieldwork, streambed prospecting, or backyard testing.</p><p><strong data-start=\"514\" data-end=\"534\">What's Included:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"535\" data-end=\"672\">\n<li data-start=\"535\" data-end=\"555\">\n<p data-start=\"537\" data-end=\"555\">(1) 10\" Gold Pan</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"556\" data-end=\"576\">\n<p data-start=\"558\" data-end=\"576\">(1) 12\" Gold Pan</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"577\" data-end=\"625\">\n<p data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"625\">(1) Snuffer Bottle (5\" tall with travel cap)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"672\">\n<p data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"672\">(1) 11\" Prospecting Scoop with Rubber Grip</p>\n</li>\n</ul><p>The gold pans are crafted from heavy-duty plastic and feature deep riffles on one side and fine riffles on the other for maximum gold retention. Each pan includes a built-in hanging hole - perfect for attaching to your pack for easy transport.</p><p>The high-quality snuffer bottle is designed for superior suction with a tight seal and precision tube - perfect for extracting even the smallest gold flakes from your pan.</p><p>Rounding out the kit is a rugged nylon scoop with a rubberized thumb grip and bright orange handle for high visibility. It’s non-metallic, so it won’t interfere with metal detectors - an excellent tool for detecting and digging!</p><p>Whether you're just starting out or upgrading your gear, this compact kit includes all the essentials to help you uncover gold wherever your adventure takes you.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2025</p></div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"><table></table>\n        </div>\n",
